title: pm profile list/show/apply merges extension-registered profiles with source labels
description: "Core resolver in profile-presets.ts that merges BUILTIN_PROFILES with extension-registered ProjectProfileDefinitions, attaching a source (builtin | package name). Builtin names reserved: extension collisions warn + are ignored; duplicate extension names: first wins + warn. profile.ts CLI threads getActiveExtensionRegistrations()?.profiles into list/show/apply and surfaces the source in output (CLI + MCP pm_profile)."
